N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4025.20 - Where entries made

State Regulations

In the absence of notice to the contrary, entries due
on the eve of and during a meeting, are due at the office of the clerk of the
course where the race is to be run. Notes
